name: DPC CN Division I Spring Tour - 2021/2022 presented by Perfect World Esports
description: Organized and produced by Perfect World Esports, DPC China Division I is the official top-level competition for China in Valve's DOTA Pro Circuit. Top teams in Division I compete for spots at the Major and ultimately TI. Representing the global standard in DOTA 2 professional play, the DPC Leagues are capped by the DPC Majors and ultimately The International. DOTA2职业巡回赛—中国联赛是由完美世界电竞主办，VALVE官方指定的DOTA2官方顶级联赛。每赛季，参与S级联赛的队伍将会竞争前往当季Major的名额以及前往TI的积分。赛事旨在锻造全球DOTA2职业生态的核心赛事体系，为各大战队英雄逐鹿，共同争夺国际邀请赛参赛名额提供了宏大的舞台。
